DosBoot is a perl script meant to detect and block the sources of a DoS attack.
It will use either apf, csf or iptables (in that order of preference) to block
the attack IPs.


Usage:  dosboot.pl OPTIONS

Options:

--genwhitelist,-g	Regenerate the automatic whitelist
	CAUTION: This will overwrite the current whitelist

--help,-h	Print this helpful help message

--list,-l	Print out list of connected IPs and the number of open connections

--maxban=n	Maximum number of IPs to ban before removing old bans

--maxcon=n	Maximum number of connections before banning IP
